#

Smashed Chickpea Toast

10 min
$5
350 kcal
Difficulty: 10%
Servings: 2

Allergens:

Chickpeas

Dietary Tags:

VegetarianVeganGluten-Free

Cuisine:

AmericanMediterranean

Course:

SnackLight Meal

Tags:

QuickHealthySnackEasy

Description

A quick, healthy, and delicious toast topped with creamy smashed chickpeas, perfect for a snack or light meal!

Ingredients

  • canned chickpeas: 1 can (15 oz)
  • lemon juice: 2 tablespoons
  • olive oil: 1 tablespoon
  • garlic powder: 1/2 teaspoon
  • salt: to taste
  • pepper: to taste
  • whole grain bread: 2 slices
  • fresh parsley (optional): for garnish
